  Once data has return 
There are two ways of generating keys 


One way ---> ssh-keygen -t rsa -b 4096 -f ~/.ssh/id_rsa
Now created the ssh-key of my userid

Second way :

root@ip-172-31-10-155:~# ssh-keygen -t rsa -C "bukkekiranb11@gmail.com"
